This is a placeholder for the Hyvo Stream Studio macOS installer.

To get the actual installer:
1. Build the desktop app using: npm run build && npx cap sync electron
2. Navigate to electron/ directory
3. Run: npm run build:mac
4. Copy the generated installer here

For now, use the web version at: https://hyvo.ai/studio

Version: 1.0.0
Platform: macOS 11.0 or later
